<h1>Will's Library!</h1>

<p>This is my fake library generated using Rails and Faker</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Books</strong>: Includes title, description, published date, and associations with authors and categories.</li>
  <li><strong>Authors</strong>: Contains the author's name, biography, and birthdate.</li>
  <li><strong>Categories</strong>: Lists different genres for categorizing books.</li>
</ul>

<p>I used the Faker gem to generate sample data for demonstration purposes, creating over 200 entries across all tables.</p>

